PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Consumer and Corporate Affairs of Jacques Girard, of Pont-Rouge, Quebec, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Guy Racine, whose term has expired.
